org.uispec4j.interception

Class InterceptionTestCase

  • java.lang.Object
    • junit.framework.Assert
      • junit.framework.TestCase
        • org.uispec4j.utils.UnitTestCase
          • org.uispec4j.interception.InterceptionTestCase
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    junit.framework.Test
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BasicHandlerTest, FileChooserHandlerTest, MainClassAdapterTest, PopupMenuInterceptionTest, PopupMenuInterceptorTest, WindowInterceptionTest, WindowInterceptorTestCase

    public abstract class InterceptionTestCase
extends UnitTestCase
    TestCase which automatically enables UISpec4J's interception mechanism.

    This test case is useful when the default toolkit has already been initialized before an UISpec4J test was run.
